name: 12FLtEHXP6R3GRipPxSjusRH2S2aT2cbaM
title: NASA APOD
body: NASA Astronomy Video of the Day Hurricane Season Animated YouTube Link https www youtube com embed h1eRp0EGOmE rel 0 showinfo 0 If video won t play here Right click Open in new tab Where do hurricanes go To better understand dangerous storms NASA compiled data from several satellites into a supercomputer simulation of this past year s hurricane season Specifically the featured video shows how smoke white sea salt blue and dust brown tracked from 2017 August through October across the northern half of Earth s Western Hemisphere These aerosols usefully trace sometimes invisible winds In the midst of the many mesmerizing flows hurricanes can be seen swirling across the Atlantic Ocean on the right Some of these hurricanes lashed islands and coastal regions in North America before dissipating in the northern Atlantic Studying this year s weather patterns may bolster more accurate storm forecasts as soon as next year Follow APOD on Facebook Google Plus Instagram or Twitter

name: 12zcXs88vJU3vaM91d2xqeChjT45rV6ZqF
title: 上海青幫
body: 首頁 下單 任務價格 如何運作 安全 疑問解答 新聞 關於零網 聯係青幫 防僞認證 上海青幫成立于清朝末期，最早是由水陸運輸行會組成的江湖幫會，宗旨是幫助窮苦人，行俠仗義，不受外人欺侮。青幫興旺于20世紀前二十年，以張嘯林、黃金榮、杜月笙爲祖師，門下弟子一度達數萬人。20世紀三四十年代，隨着戰爭的爆發，青幫逐漸式微，至中共竊取民國政權后消亡。 21世紀以來，藉助電子加密網絡技術的應用，青幫這一古老江湖幫會重獲新生，上海青幫立足上海，輻射全國，爲廣大苦難百姓竭誠服務。現任青幫幫主无燈大師，具有豐富的實戰技術與經驗，青幫在无燈的引領下，必能發揚光大，重振幫威！ 青幫的使命是幫助成千上萬受冤屈的百姓施行天道，重獲公平正義！受苦受屈的人們在報仇血恨的同時，免於暴露自己。 中國現時的法律，無法爲人民提供保護，人民在中共的暴政統治下毫無安全感，警察公然殺害平民的事例頻頻發生。中國雖然有法律，等于沒有法律，中共官匪勾結，魚肉百姓，貪贜枉法的情形隨處可見，法律衹是爲保護中共權貴階級利益、維護中共統治而制定的游戲。一些百姓被官府欺壓后，無處申冤，維權者辛苦上訪卻被打成刁民，甚至被施以重刑迫害。而普通民衆受到不法侵害后，因對方的權勢或財力，施害者逃脫法律制裁、被輕判的現象比比皆是。 青幫在此爲這些受苦人民提供一個平臺，受苦受冤的百姓從此不必再求助于官府和法律，你們自己就是法官，可以爲自己的冤屈做出裁決！你們可以在這裏下單，雇傭殺手除掉與你們有血海深仇的人。同時，這裏也爲想求財的江湖人士提供一個賺錢途徑，有能力也急需用錢的人可以在這裏接單，完成任務后即可領取酬金。青幫根據不同的目標，對標的制定合理的價格。 青幫的用戶分爲兩類，青幫客戶和青幫成員。客戶指有報仇服務需要的人，可以注冊成青幫客戶，提供目標信息，發佈任務，下單，等待殺手接單。青幫成員指願意違法或願意提供殺人服務，借此道賺錢的人，在正式成爲青幫弟子后，可以瀏覽任務，接單。 任務的酬勞及交易以比特幣方式支付。客戶下單后，將酬勞轉到自己的比特幣賬戶，由青幫暫爲擔保，殺手完成任務后，酬勞將支付到殺手的比特幣賬戶，如果殺手未完成任務，預付款將退還客戶。這種交易方式比請現實殺手有優勢，現實中若找殺手，殺手通常會收取50 預付款，有些殺手收到預付款后并不辦事。 青幫、客戶和俠士 殺手 這三者間皆無實際接觸，三方之中的任一方都無法獲得另兩方的真實信息，杜絕任何一方出問題的風險。若現實中請殺

title: Smite Chow Blog Demo
body: Use Nginx to Step Up Generic Proxy Server 2016 02 28T17 21 00 08 00 再见理想 In my case i want to have a generic proxy server to proxy some static asserts which had been reseted by China GFW Give a detail example SwitchyOmega is famous proxy client on Chrome theres an option you can set for Auto Proxy you need provide a url so that SwitchyOmega can auto download from it The good news is that theres already exist a service on github to provide a rule file called gfwlist gfwlist but the bad news is github some times not reachable because of the GFW so if you have a proxy server you can just use it to proxy github file Here is my solution for that https go dist pub raw githubusercontent com gfwlist gfwlist master gfwlist txt You can see the origin url just follow a domain name its simple and powerful Also i setup a magic on schema it will go through to the destination server What does it mean It means the middle proxy server will request to github follow the origin request schema like below https raw githubusercont

name: 13TL1Grj6fwLXRGxiYPjpTFZqWqFsVZhox
title: How to create a website on ZeroNet
body: How to make a site on Zeronet Stop Zeronet Open the Zeronet folder It s the one with the data log plugins folders in it Open a command window here In Windows hold CTRL and right click for the option Run the following command to create a new site structure python zeronet py siteCreate Copy and Save the address and private key or you won t be able to edit the site Type yes and press enter to continue Now edit the site under your zeronet data your address folder To sign the site ready to publish simply run python zeronet py siteSign your address You will have to paste your private key for authentication If anyone else is seeding your site you can run this to force a publish python zeronet py sitePublish your address

title: 二木子布
body: 昵称：二木子布 数字id：2095599540 地区：北京 简介：一条哈士奇，画💛图，更百合相关，日常更新麻杆和大奶，工作约稿请联系个人邮箱：futaki bu@outlook com 微博图请勿转载谢谢 ´ ▽ ﾉ 更新地址：http weibo wbdacdn com user 2095599540 头像： 好友 粉丝 微博 下载 696 55 9089 1350 1559 http t cn RapHF7r 记得夸我 ​通过 iPhone 62017 05 15 00 08 23 转发42次 评论303次 赞884次 点击查看 微博原文 #一元cp# #一元couple#喝高的代表 二哈 二哈 二哈 ​ 通过 微博 weibo com2017 05 13 07 24 03 转发440次 评论482次 赞3885次 点击查看 微博原文 又是幸福的一天 ​点击看大图通过 iPhone 62017 05 13 00 47 20 转发14次 评论164次 赞2411次 点击查看 微博原文 我日，刚刚在地铁里，因为快要没车了所以和九三一路快跑。正跑着前面一个妹子掏钱包，眼睁睁看着她钱包里飘出一张毛爷爷！！我一手就给抄着了…！一把又给她塞回钱包里，冲她一笑：“不用谢！” 吗的。装完逼就跑真刺激。 ​通过 iPhone 62017 05 12 23 24 48 转发26次 评论164次 赞2887次 点击查看 微博原文 幸福的一天 ​点击看大图通过 iPhone 62017 05 11 22 32 34 转发22次 评论180次 赞1975次 点击查看 微博原文 http t cn RaxQZtq 哈哈哈哈哈是不是很意外～ ​通过 iPhone 62017 05 11 02 07 06 转发34次 评论394次 赞910次 点击查看 微博原文 发布了头条文章：《随心而欲所不能求【纯属虚构！】》 睡前写的一个小故事正式更名，谢谢大家一直以来的支持！预祝阅读愉快 http t cn RaMdzGe ​通过 微博 weibo com2017 05 10 20 44 29 转发36次 评论262次 赞761次 点击查看 微博原文 自从九三开始实习上班…我每天起床都会看到面前的桌子上有个保温杯，但是我从来都没碰过它。今天大姨妈实在不想下床，就随手拿了起来，发现居然是满的………我抱着试一试的心情打开，里面居然是现成的温开水！ ​

name: 147AsJCihV923F2VXnswwRUYDfjRDDDmyZ
title: iiKB Zeronet Proxy
body: ignore this shit and just go to hello zero english português contact contato This is it We ve been running this zeronet gateway for a long time We re probably the oldest gateway or proxy like you kids call it still online Turns out that the maintainers ran out of money and the server in which this gateway is hosted is limited We have to choose between keeping the other anarchist services we already provide or this zeronet gateway alone If you want to see this gateway online send love to 1MYgx5P5fB4553H6Ca2EKGrGe2tp4bJ726 We use this gateway a lot and we also want it to continue existing But it is not on our hands alone anymore Sincerely iiKB admins UPDATE Do you often see 502 Bad Gateway when you access zeronet iikb org Even though the crontab checks if zeronet is down and is trying to restart the service every minute therefore consuming even more processing power the zeronet service keeps going down This means that we need to move to another server which would cost money You get the idea É agora Nós estamos

title: TED Talk 2017 - Speakers List Archive
description: An archive of the TED Speakers before they removed people.
body: Home Program Speakers Speakers Learn more about the speaker lineup for TED2017 Adam Alter Psychologist Session 9 It s Personal What makes us incessantly check our phones Adam Alter dives into the fascinating psychology that drives our tech addictions Adam Alter s academic research focuses on judgment decision making and social psychology with a particular interest in the sometimes surprising effects of subtle cues in the environment on human cognition and behavior He is the bestselling author of two books Irresistible which considers why so many people today are addicted to so many behaviors from incessant smart phone and internet use to video game playing and online shopping and Drunk Tank Pink which investigates how hidden forces in the world around us shape our thoughts feelings and behaviors adamalterauthor com @adamleealter Ashton Applewhite Author activist Session 10 Tales of Tomorrow Ashton Applewhite asks us to look at ageism the assumption that older people are alike and that aging impoverishes us I

title: BitcoinPrice
description: Fetch the Bitcoin price through ZeroNet.
body: BitcoinPrice This site is for fetching the BTC price through ZeroNet programmatically The price is updated every 15 minutes by a script and uses averages of the major bitcoin exchanges to determine the current price Instructions You can programmatically fetch the price json file and parse its contents using any JSON compliant library Donate If you like the service and would like to keep it running you can donate some Bitcoins to the following address 1AmSbjSgRLGA8QuCdMMhQtpGNu4wfiTeGE Contact Want to tell me something that s on your mind or you want me to improve the service Then shoot me a message using Bitmessage BM 2cX2K7aHCfznXuS1DVYwzxy4m4u4HpssoR

name: 15AGz4VzK4Sowkoahoj9VijzHPnjV28ZDM
title: ZeroNet 中文文档
body: ZeroNet 中文文档 介绍 ZeroNet 是什么 为什么要使用 功能 它是如何工作的 有关 ZeroNet 加密 内容更新 多用户站点的幻灯片 » 截图 更多截图 » 目前的不足 帮助这个项目 感谢您 常见问题 开始使用 ZeroNet 安装 示例站点 创建新站点 站点开发 入门 ZeroFrame API 参考 content json 文件结构 dbschema json 文件结构 帮助 ZeroNet 开发 为 ZeroNet 做贡献 网络协议 捐赠 ZeroNet 中文文档 文档 » 介绍 在 GitHub 编辑 ZeroNet 是什么 ZeroNet 使用 Bitcoin 加密算法以及 BitTorrent 技术以建立一个 分布式抗审查的网络 用户可以发布静态或动态网站到 ZeroNet 访问者可以选择共享这个网站 网站将会一直在线即使只有一个节点在共享 每当一个站点被所有者更新 所有共享它的节点 访问过此网站的人 将只会收到网站内容的增量更新 ZeroNet 带有一个内置的 SQL 数据库 这让内容很多 content heavy 的站点更容易开发 这个数据库也会与共享它的节点增量同步 为什么要使用 我们相信开放 自由 无审查的网络 没有审查 一旦发布就无法删除 不会受单点故障影响 内容将保持在线即使只有一个节点 无法关闭 节点无处不在 内容由用户自愿共享 Content is served by any user who wishes to 迅速 ZeroNet 使用 BitTorrent 技术使内容发送快过中心化的服务器 离线工作 即使互联网不可用时也可以访问站点 安全 内容所有权 Content ownership 是使用和 Bitcoin wallet 相同的加密算法加密的 功能 简单 无需配置即可运行 无需密码的基于 BIP32 的认证 使用和 Bitcoin wallet 相同的加密算法来保护你的账号 实时更新站点 Namecoin bit 域名支持 SQL 数据库支持 让站点开发更简单并且加快页面加载 匿名 完整的 Tor 网络支持通过 onion 隐藏服务 onion hidden services 而不是 ipv4 地址 TLS 加密连接 自动 UPnP 端口转发 多用户 开放代理 插件支持 在任何浏览器 操作系统上工作 它是如何工作的 在你安装并运行 ZeroNet 后 浏

name: 15F9LYs6c17NUXv3MxpJSGbpWxyHTEbzMk
title: NinjaBeats - WIP
body: Introducing Free music for all Scroll down for more info A new take on music streaming I know that there s already lots of music streaming services out there so we wanted to try something entirely new a decentralised distribution platform for artists and fans alike With NinjaBeats anyone can get their music out there to the public and anyone can listen to content on NinjaBeats for free sometimes even without counting towards your data plan As we re a distribution intemediary platform we don t have the restrictions that plauge current music streaming services without compromising anyone s rights We believe that it shouldn t matter where you are or what you re using if you re a fan of an artist and they release a new song why should the device you use stop you Why should it matter what country you re in Why do you have to pay extra for slightly better bitrate lossy audio These never used to be problems with CDs so why have all these restrictions been put in place for online content that you can t even download

name: 15gfg6DUVkp7ApLSMQvC2ig5qy8j91jXeW
title: 编程随想的博客镜像
body: 编程随想的博客 ★关于 你看到的这个博客离线版本，制作于 2016 03 21（正常情况下，每个月都会更新，以包含俺博客上的所有博文）。 ◇如何获取俺博客的【离线电子书】 要想【自动】获取俺博客的离线版本，请使用 BT Sync 进行自动同步。 BT Sync 的同步密钥是 B7P64IMWOCXWEYOXIMBX6HN5MHEULFS4V 不熟悉 BT Sync 的同学，请看俺写的教程《扫盲 BT Sync》。 ◇电子书格式说明 HTML 格式 不管你用的是哪个操作系统，只要你装了浏览器，就可以直接浏览。 首先，确保你已经完成 BT Sync 的同步（在界面上，该同步目录的图标变为绿色）。 浏览的时候，先进入 BT Sync 同步目录下的“blog”目录，然后再进入“html”目录，双击 index html 就可以打开离线浏览的首页。 备注： html 目录下所有网页的交叉链接，都转换为【相对路径】。因此，你可以把整个 html 目录复制到其它电脑；也可以用压缩软件打包，然后分享给其他人。 CHM 格式 “CHM 格式”需要你手动制作（别怕，俺提供了傻瓜化的“一键式生成”），具体步骤如下： 1 首先，确保你已经完成 BT Sync 的同步（在界面上，该同步目录的图标变为绿色）。 2 使用 Windows 系统的同学，进入如下目录： blog\make\chm 并双击 make chm wsf 3 使用 Linux Unix 系统的同学，进入如下目录： blog make chm 并运行 Python 脚本 make chm py（该脚本同时兼容 Python2 和 Python3） 备注： 不使用 Windows 系统的同学，可以参考维基百科的“这个页面”列出了“非Windows”下的 CHM 阅读软件。 EPUB 格式 “EPUB 格式”需要你手动制作（别怕，俺提供了傻瓜化的“一键式生成”），具体步骤如下： 1 首先，确保你已经完成 BT Sync 的同步（在界面上，该同步目录的图标变为绿色）。 2 使用 Windows 系统的同学，进入如下目录： blog\make\epub 并双击 make epub wsf 3 使用 Linux Unix 系统的同学，进入如下目录： blog make epub 并运行 Python 脚本 make epub py（该脚本同时兼容 Python2 和 Python3

name: 15JScXCxfgcFisufEXAxdJa8RLXEoc66Rv
title: huoju.bit - huoju's blog
body: Huo Ju home archives Huo Ju home archives 李笑来，那个一顿饭点8条鲈鱼的人 2017 09 09 我已经记不清到底哪年认识的李笑来，大概是2006年吧。到现在已经超过10年了。这10年间我看着他做过无数事情，聊过很多想法。今天笑来变成了众矢之的，似乎所有事情都怪他，很多文章干脆把他描述成一个处心积虑的骗子的文章。但李笑来究竟如何想，他的逻辑是什么，没有一篇文章写过。当然，他们没采访过李笑来，没读过他的文章，怎么能解释这些问题呢？我想，与其让别人来批判他，不如由我这个熟悉他的人来吧。 李笑来有太多想法和行为是不合常理的，我非常理解他会被人们误会。从我认识他的第一天，就明白了他肯定是个有争议的人物。我们第一次见面是在一家川菜馆吃饭，那顿饭至今难忘，因为桌上有个人点菜的方式太奇怪了。我们一共4个人，这家伙点了8份豆干，4盘回锅肉，正常人哪有这么点菜的？他的逻辑倒是很简单，既然这个好吃，为什么不多点几份？全然不顾普通人点菜的习惯是不会点重复的菜。这个人就是李笑来。我想了想他的逻辑，觉得确实是合理的。但是大多数人未必会接受这种逻辑，更不会仔细考虑是不是他这样做有道理，只会觉得他太不正常了，更别说之后几年他展现了更奇怪的点菜法：请8个人在“美炉村”吃饭，直接点了8条纸包鲈鱼，每人一条，其他什么菜都没点。 一直到今天，李笑来做过的事情我都是大致能理解的。虽然他做的事情有一些我认同，另外一些不认同，但无论是否认同，我都理解他到底为什么这样做。所有的事情都跟他点菜一样，看上去离经叛道甚至荒唐，但如果真的认真仔细推敲，又合乎逻辑，产生这种错位只是因为他对很多事情看法甚至很多东西的基础概念，都是不同于大多数人的。 more 写了一个Hexo的评论插件 2017 08 06 Zeronet默认的Blog系统Zeroblog太单一了。实际上Zeronet就是一堆静态页面，网站的拥有者签名之后，用BT协议共享给大家。所以我用Hexo来建了这个blog。 但是Zeroblog是支持评论的，Hexo当然没有。我读了下文档又看了看代码，半移植半写的把它的评论功能复制到了Hexo生成的页面上。 代码和说明都放在Github上了。做这个的过程中顺便也看了Zeronet实现动态功能的办法：通过javascript调用Zeronet framework来写本地文件，然后mapping到一个sqlite库里面，这

body: HTML5 Sudoku In this demo we take the well known game of Sudoku and demonstrate how developers can use HTML5 and JavaScript to create an efficient algorithm to solve these puzzles The algorithms draw heavily on the Chakra engine’s support for ECMAScript 5 standard array operations to rapidly solve many Sudoku games You can also manually solve Sudoku puzzles # of Games 1000 5000 10000 Solving puzzles Finished In 6 4 2 8 9 8 2 4 8 3 1 9 6 9 5 1 8 1 4 2 3 5 8 9 5 6 2 9 7 8 5 1 9 8 5 6 Level Easy Medium Hard Very Hard Insane MISTAKE FOUND LOOKIN GOOD YOU WIN Great job Can you do it again

description: Site que explica como a Zero net funciona em Portugues Brasil
body: Introdução O que é a ZeroNet Porque a ZeroNet existe Funcionalidades Como funciona Limitações Atuais Zero Sites Torrent Buscadores Como criar Zero Sites O que é a ZeroNet A ZeroNet usa a mesma Cryptografia e Blockchain da Bitcoin junto com a tecnologia de distribuição de dados do BitTorrent para criar uma internet descentralizada e resistente a censura Os usuários podem publicar sites estáticos ou dinâmicos na ZeroNet e os visitantes podem optar em servir o website Sites permanecerá online mesmo se ele esteja sendo servido por apenas um peer Quando um site é atualizado pelo seu proprietário todos os nós que servem esse site visitantes anteriores receberá apenas as atualizações incrementais feitas ao conteúdo do site ZeroNet conta com um banco de dados SQL integrado Isso faz com que o desenvolvimento de content heavy sites fácil O Banco de Dados é também sincroniza com a hospedagem com a ZeroNet atualização incremental Porque a ZeroNet existe A ZeroNet acredita em uma internet aberta livre e sem censura na su

body: libzeronet Sec minimal performance oriented POSIX portable C implementation of the Zeronet content sharing protocol This is the home for the future libzeronet software project by Vincent Olivier It is a POSIX C implementation of ZeroNet basic I O RAM FS NET that radically focuses on portability within the POSIX ecosystem anonymity security performance and separation of concerns For now it will not replicate the ZeroNet Python implementation in its entirety and a fork that wraps around libzeronet for full functionality is also in the works By default it will only support connections to peers and trackers via Tor I will need testers that can undersdand C within a POSIX environment so please inbox me if you are interested Discussion here here and incidently here UPDATE 2016 06 28 the Python ZeroNet reference implementation uses Gevent and libzeronet will use libuv which has significantly more fuctionalities than libev upon which Gevent is based notably for filesystem I O Larger file support being my main immedi

name: 17AbM7qdS9jHqtg2uPmutU586T569yJoSX
title: CyberWald
body: Willkommen im CyberWald Der Treffpunkt für IT Begeisterte Menschen im Westerwald IMPRESSUM KONTAKT Cyberwald Homepage July 22 2017 Es mag nicht sofort auffallen aber unsere CyberWald Homepage unterscheidet sich stark von vielen anderen Seiten im Internet Die CyberWald Homepage wird über das “Inter Planetary File System” IPFS gehostet Das bedeutet dass unsere Homepage nicht auf einem zentralen Server liegt sondern über ein Peer to Peer Netzwerk verteilt wird Bei einem P 2 P Netzwerk tauschen die teilnehmenden Rechner die Daten direkt aus und brauchen dafür keinen zentralen Server Ruft man unsere Homepage über das IPFS Netzwerk auf dann kann die Webseite von überall auf der Welt übertragen werden Weiterlesen… Willkommen July 22 2017 Hallo und Willkommen auf unserer Homepage Wir suchen IT Begeisterte Menschen im Westerwald für gemeinsame Treffen und IT Projekte Unsere Homepage befindet sich noch im Aufbau aber bald werden die ersten Inhalte folgen und auch Informationen wo Treffen stattfinden Recent Posts Cyber

title: Zero Censorship
description: Software tools for getting around censorship
body: Lantern Open Internet for everyone Lantern is a free desktop application that delivers fast reliable and secure access to the open Internet for users in censored regions It uses a variety of techniques to stay unblocked including P2P and domain fronting Lantern relies on users in uncensored regions acting as access points to the open Internet Android OSX 10 8 and Above Ubuntu 14 04 32 Bit Ubuntu 14 04 64 Bit Windows XP SP3 and Above

name: 17WKedkX8qMdS9tUzYn4dwox4gKsGdwX9q
title: Festival Latinoamericano de Software Libre
body: Toggle navigation FLISOL Comunidad Noticias FLISOL Festival Latinoamericano de Software Libre Noticias Feb 22 Confirmacion de evento el 23 de Abril Sobre FLISOL El FLISoL es el evento de difusión de Software Libre más grande en Latinoamérica y está dirigido a todo tipo de público estudiantes académicos empresarios trabajadores funcionarios públicos entusiastas y aun personas que no poseen mucho conocimiento informático El FLISoL se realiza desde el año 2005 y desde el 2008 se adoptó su realización el 4to Sábado de abril de cada año La entrada es gratuita y su principal objetivo es promover el uso del software libre dando a conocer al público en general su filosofía alcances avances y desarrollo El evento es organizado por las diversas comunidades locales de Software Libre y se desarrolla simultáneamente con eventos en los que se instala de manera gratuita y totalmente legal software libre en las computadoras que llevan los asistentes Además en forma paralela se ofrecen charlas ponencias y talleres sobre temá

name: 18prXQSzFxhxeRtbAYxAdpqDh4uy7skX6Z
title: 表白
body: 某某： 我爱你 只有在你的微笑里，我才有呼吸，还贪恋着你的风情，诱惑着你的神秘，埋葬了我的爱情，脉脉之情如一溪春水，快刀难斩断，随着天各一方的时间越来越长，我的思念也越来越深，我很想找一个万籁俱寂的深夜或一个阳光明媚的早晨，把许多心底的惆怅、寂寞向你倾诉。 某某，我们的故事是最感人，最真实的，早安，我永恒的爱人，虽然我尚未起床，但思想已经飞到你的身边来了，不管今世也好来世也好，我所要的只有你。我要与你同坐在有着月光的草坪上，一起遥望着繁星点缀的夜空，讲述那人间古老的爱情神话。人生不止，寂寞不已。寂寞人生爱无休，寂寞是爱永远的主题。 某某，在这没有月的漆黑的夜里，我独自坐在窗前写着这封信，希望睡前可以吻你；希望睡时可以抱着你；希望醒来可以看到你，有你的日子，一切都是那么美好，风和日丽，鲜花遍地；没你的日子，白昼是那么的黯淡，黑夜是那么的漫长。你的话已经锁在我的记忆里了，那钥匙你就替我保管一辈子吧。如果你冷，我将你拥入怀中；如果你哭，我替你擦去泪痕。你像那天边的云，飘泊不定，叫人难以追寻；你像那水中的萍，流移四方，叫我难以琢磨。这样的习惯也是一种甜蜜的负担，思念你早已成为我生活中不可缺少的习惯。思念就像河流般，滔滔不绝地流向大海，流向我的心房，当我闭上双眼，你的身影又浮现在我的眼前，一些路我们并肩走过，一些故事我们就是主人公，一首歌我们对唱了那么久，永远不变的是心中深藏的对爱的执着。如果，我只有一天的生命，我会去找你，并告诉你，我是如此的依恋你。我们那两颗充满柔情和陶醉的心永远在一起，我愿做天上的星星，给你永恒的光芒，永远守候在你身边。盼你在每一次想你的瞬间，爱你在每一秒呼吸的间隙。不知为什么，只要有你在我身边，我的心便不再惶惶不安。有你的日子你就是一切，没你的日子一切都是你。 某某，我想告诉你，自从有了你，我觉得整个世界都在向我点头微笑，你那充满朝气的身影总是伴着月光入我梦来，让我牵挂不停。还记得我俩的初遇。那一瞬间，时间就像静止了一般，你的气质让我觉得惊喜，认识你我的生活充满生机，爱上你我的生活充满激情。 某某，保留一个最浪漫的故事，给你一声祝福，一个kiss，爱你直到永远！ 某某，理解我吗？我不是弱智，但我会傻傻的爱你到永远。某某，我只想和你白头到老，美轮美奂的你编织着神话，创造着奇迹，只因让我遇到你。接受我，好吗？ www 51bbw cn 我要表白网2013 08 12 某某 这是我们认识的第 永远爱你，

title: Tic Computer
body: × Select a file to add to the computer TIC tiny computer v0 14 0 dev status IN DEVELOPMENT http tic computer c Copyright 2017 Nesbox Author Vadim Grigoruk grigoruk@gmail com Bug tracker https github com nesbox tic computer issues ABOUT TIC is a tiny computer where you can make play and share tiny games There are built in tools for development code sprites maps sound editors and the command line which is enough to create a mini retro game At the exit you will get a cartridge file which can be stored and played on the website Also the game can packed into a player that works on all popular platforms and distribute as you wish To make a retro styled game the whole process of creation takes place under some technical limitations 240x136 pixels display 16 color palette 256 8x8 color sprites 4 channel sound and etc SPECIFICATION Display 240x136 pixels 16 colors palette Input 2 gamepads with 6 buttons Sprites 256 8x8 foreground sprites and 256 8x8 background tiles Map 240x136 cells 1920x1088 pixels Sound 4 channels

title: Punkcoder Zeronet Site
body: Punkcoder Zeronet Site Main Menu Home Links About Social Networks All Posts Offline Zeronet @punkcoder · Sep 21 2017 · 2 min read So I ran a bit of an experiment I was running zeronet is an offline mode and I noticed that there are some sites that are severly broken in a full offline state For me it’s a matter of taking the train but it’s important to note the opperation of a network of communications in the attempt of a full government shutdown such as the one that was seen in Turkey in 2016 Read More → Zeronet Build Out With Hugo @punkcoder · Sep 19 2017 · 2 min read After going through and working with zeronet for a while I thought I would share the process for getting a site up and running without the standard clone site Hugo similar to Jekyll is a fairly good option for doing this kinds of site since they create static sites I originally went out looking for solutions to create new sites I kept running into the “Get Started Quickly” process provided by the clone site button Read More → Hello Zeronet @pu

body: 昵称：棉花和aumi 数字id：1142158300 地区：其他 简介：晒猫 kame リぶ 更新地址：http weibo wbdacdn com user 1142158300 头像： 好友 粉丝 微博 下载 80 2 3039 650 690 哦 这样我开评论你们可以集中在这条PO喷 摊手 零零散散的你们不够解气嘛 反正电话对峙也不接没什么想说了的 摊手 以后不再回应 ​通过 微博 weibo com2小时前 转发385次 评论1272次 赞182次 点击查看 微博原文 @12dora 挂电话？听说您在直播带节奏？敢不敢直播和我电话对峙？ 指天发誓说你没有摔断我的猫的腿？敢不敢和我去找潘医生对峙？ ​通过 iPhone 64小时前 转发494次 评论1119次 赞173次 点击查看 微博原文 以下是石先生提及的房子，收据以及银行账单和他没有半毛钱关系。满足你们转账记录我贴了。那么请对方提供一下你所谓的赠与我180万房款记录？如果你说你带着现金给我的，请晒出你的收据和签字？你是不是想说送给我的没想要收据那您还真情圣。还有所谓我编造你打断棉花的腿的事情也请你对着猫的在天之灵发毒誓不是你做的。肝炎是断腿后手术后的病症谢谢。你们所谓2月和我出去看电影的小男生3月25还没有正式交往直到4月10号刚回国，我大概是和鬼去看的。洗地粉们双标玩的就是6啊，怎么不洗石先生自己勾搭的女粉？就是因为你们瞎起哄要我们复合，搞得人家还要为了照顾女友情绪怼我给我强行扣锅，昨天一边对我深情告白一边还要和女粉卿卿我我真是辛苦您了。电话打码了免得你们说我精分开小号。至于黑子喷我伪装受伤，你们太看得起我了4 12号就预料到一个月后的事往手上画伪妆还跟朋友做聊天记录伪造。假惺惺的跟粉丝讲别来骂我然后反手就点赞一波演技真好。点击看大图通过 微博 weibo com2017 05 18 22 28 23 转发2370次 评论4073次 赞907次 点击查看 微博原文 哦 才发现TGP截图完全看不清楚 补发在转发和评论里 http t cn Ra8gzuD 棉花和aumi 来自 微博 weibo com 2017 05 18 昨天一晚上没， 刚醒起来讲一下重点。#aumi#既然都在搜索我就加个TAG ​ 查看大图 4589 3130 1252 通过 微博 weibo com2017 05 18 19 43 52 转发203次 评论305次 赞60次

body: git the simple guide just a simple guide for getting started with git setup Download git for OSX Download git for Windows Download git for Linux create a new repository create a new directory open it and perform a git init to create a new git repository checkout a repository create a working copy of a local repository by running the command git clone path to repository when using a remote server your command will be git clone username@host path to repository workflow your local repository consists of three trees maintained by git the first one is your Working Directory which holds the actual files the second one is the Index which acts as a staging area and finally the HEAD which points to the last commit you ve made add commit You can propose changes add it to the Index using git add filename git add This is the first step in the basic git workflow To actually commit these changes use git commit m Commit message Now the file is committed to the HEAD but not in your remote repository yet pushing changes Your

body: AmayaOS Sistema Operativo libre de tipo UNIX Inicio Sobre AmayaOS ¿Qué es AmayaOS AmayaOS es un sistema operativo similar a UNIX que es software libre y respeta tu libertad Puedes instalar AmayaOS en tu ordenador sin temor alguno ¡Es 100 software libre El proyecto AmayaOS se inció en 2014 para hacer un nuevo sistema operativo para los pc x86 de 32 bits AmayaOS no es GNULinux AmayaOS no es un derivado de Linux ni de GNU ni siquiera es una distro GNULinux AmayaOS es un sistema operativo con desarrollo independiente basado en FreeNOS Free Niek s Operating System http www freenos org AmayaOS sigue la filosofía UNIX® Filosofia UNIX en Español Unix philosophy ¿Cuáles son los fines del proyecto Crear un sistema operativo capaz de correr fluido con tan solo 16 MegaBytes de memoria RAM ¿Qué es el software libre El software libre es aquel que cumple con las 4 libertades de la filosofía del software libre y estas libertades permiten a los usuarios tener el control de su informática tanto individual como colectiva Softw

title: Alien's Zone
body: Alien s Zone Alien的地盘 Home Archives 把Zero的评论功能添加进来了 2016 11 10 感觉现在文档还是太少了，说得不详细 看了ZeroBlog的源码，现学了下coffee，勉强把ZeroBlog上的评论搬过来了 不过因为Hexo是直接生成HTML文件，文章都不是存数据库的，像feeds什么的我现在还没想到方法做 感觉ZeroNet现在的局限性还是挺大的，太不太灵活了 ZeroNet 使用Hexo在ZeroNet上发布网站 2016 11 08 在ZeroNet创建网站直接参考 中文wiki然后找到你的网站目录 安装Hexo先安装NodeJs 然后运行1npm install g hexo cli 创建博客命令行中找到一个好目录，运行1hexo init blog 配置Hexo编辑Blog下的 config yml文件 12url http 127 0 0 1 43110 网站地址 root 网站地址 1public dir ZeroNet网站所在目录路径 例如 D ZeroNet data 网站文件夹 ZeroNet Hello World 2016 11 08 Welcome to Hexo This is your very first post Check documentation for more info If you get any problems when using Hexo you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub Quick StartCreate a new post1 hexo new My New Post More info Writing Run server1 hexo server More info Server Generate static files1 hexo generate More info Generating Deploy to remote sites1 hexo deploy More info Deployment 当前已缓存 0 个节点 Proudly powered by Hexo and Theme by Hacker © 2016 Alien

name: 1B583Bw465t3ikcf7gRHrPG2tgE7kJJ3EM
title: redPanda
body: redPanda secure peer to peer chat Welcome to redPanda We are developing a peer to peer instant messaging system in our spare time It is open sourced via github com redPanda project as a library and a command line client for windows and linux written in Java The client written in Qt is currently not very stable Our main focus is the android application which you can download at the google play store For all downloads you can have a look at files redpanda im You can find installation instructions for linux and windows at install txt For questions or discussion have a look at our subreddit r redPandaProject Current prioritized working regions updated 8 21 2015 White paper improve p2p logic If you want to get more information want to join discussions or have any questions you can visit the forum forum redPanda im

body: 新内容在这 历史的伤口 your browser does not support the audio element 1 如何创建一个 ZeroNet 站点 如果 zeronet 在运行，把它关掉 执行： zeronet siteCreate Site private key 23DKQpzxhbVBrAtvLEc2uvk7DZweh4qL3fn3jpM3LgHDczMK2TtYUq 这个是你的私钥 Site address 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 （这个是你的零网地址） Site created 你已经完成了！ 现在任何人都可以通过 http localhost 43110 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 来访问你的站点 2 如何往你的站点添加内容 修改位于 data 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 的目录 这里面就是你的网站的所有内容。 可以用任何网页编辑工具添加内容。 在你改好之后 执行 zeronet siteSign 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 Signing site 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 Private key input hidden 23DKQpzxhbVBrAtvLEc2uvk7DZweh4qL3fn3jpM3LgHDczMK2TtYUq 输入你在创建站点时获得的 私钥 上面标红色的部分 3 重新发布你的站点 zeronet sitePublish 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 Site 13DNDk bhC2 Publishing to 3 10 peers Site 13DNDk bhC2 Successfuly published to 3 peers Serving files 就是这样 你现在已经成功的签名并推送了你的更改。

title: ZeroTodos
body: ZeroTodos cert user id Logout Select user Using dataUsage Select user to login click Save to save and publish any changes you made only appears after you made changes Your todos are encrypted using the encryption functionality provided by the ZeroNet API using ECIES Elliptic Curve Integrated Encryption Scheme Nothing is 100 secure developers can make mistakes so use your own judgement on what data to enter I can make no guarantees that your data is safe X todo title taskCount todo saving Saving Save task text X Cancel Delete this todo list Clear completed If you have any problems or questions feel free to send me a ZeroMail or leave a comment on my development blog

title: ZeroPGP
body: 使用 Javascript 实现的 PGP 加密服务 © 2005 2006 Herbert Hanewinkel © 2016 Aleister © 2016 Rainlime 把它折腾到了 ZeroNet 上 你可以直接使用这个页面在浏览器中来加密你的信息，而不需要安装额外的应用程序 你可以信任此服务，因为： 所有的代码都是用易读的 Javascript 编写。 你可以将页面下载下来验证它的源代码。 我们没有在页面中嵌入二进制代码，也没有从服务器加载过。 我们也没有将明文传送出去。 将对方的使用 RSA 或者 Elgamal 算法的、ASCII 格式的 PGP 公钥粘贴到这里来。 即公钥以 asc 格式导出的文件的内容 。 版本 用户 ID 公钥 ID 16 位十六进制数 公钥类型和数据 经过 AES 和 RSA Elgamal 算法加密的 PGP 消息如下 在这里输入要加密的消息 消息长度 字节。 消耗了 秒的时间。 因处理器、消息长度、公钥长度、公钥类型等缘故，使用 Javascript 加密可能需要几秒钟的时间，请耐心等候。 function getQueryVariable variable var query window location search substring 1 var vars query split for var i 0 i vars length i var pair vars i split if decodeURIComponent pair 0 variable return decodeURIComponent pair 1 return null function getQueryKey var s BEGIN PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK e END PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK var search begin end key body checksum search window location search begin search indexOf BEGIN if begin 0 return end search indexOf END begin if end 0 return end search indexOf BLOCK end if end 0 return key decodeURIComponent search

body: Toggle navigation FLISOL Comunidad Noticias FLISOL Festival Latinoamericano de Software Libre Noticias Feb 22 Confirmacion de evento el 23 de Abril Sobre FLISOL El FLISoL es el evento de difusión de Software Libre más grande en Latinoamérica y está dirigido a todo tipo de público estudiantes académicos empresarios trabajadores funcionarios públicos entusiastas y aun personas que no poseen mucho conocimiento informático El FLISoL se realiza desde el año 2005 y desde el 2008 se adoptó su realización el 4to Sábado de abril de cada año La entrada es gratuita y su principal objetivo es promover el uso del software libre dando a conocer al público en general su filosofía alcances avances y desarrollo El evento es organizado por las diversas comunidades locales de Software Libre y se desarrolla simultáneamente con eventos en los que se instala de manera gratuita y totalmente legal software libre en las computadoras que llevan los asistentes Además en forma paralela se ofrecen charlas ponencias y talleres sobre temá

body: Toggle navigation 服務供應商 避兔使用以美國與英國為基地的網路服務 虛擬私人網路 VPN 私密電郵 令狀金絲雀 加密的雲端儲存服務 分散化社交網路 域名系統 DNS 尊重用戶隱私的搜尋引撃 瀏覽器 推薦 指紋 WebRTC IP 漏洞 瀏覽器火狐隱私附加元件 相關的隱私設定調整 軟體 電郵軟體 電郵替代工具 即時通訊 影音通訊 密碼管理 檔案加密 安全的檔案同步 安全的密碼產生器 自足網路 加密貨幣 自搭的雲端伺服器 數位筆記本 Paste Services 生產力工具 不要使用Windows 10 OS作業系統 桌機筆電作業系統 光碟隨身碟開機作業系統 手機作業系統 路由器軔體 參與 分享 email轉寄 Facebook Twitter Google reddit LinkedIn StumbleUpon Diaspora Twitter 捐款贊助 你正在被人盯著。私人和國家支持的組織正在監控與記錄你的線上活動。 這裏提供一些知識與工具以保護個人隱私抵抗全球大規模監控。 Language English Español Deutsch 簡體中文 Darknet Tor I2P ZeroNet 隱私 我無不可告人之處 過去十多個月來 每當我在全球各地討論這個議題的時候 每次總是有人會這樣對我說： 我並不擔心隱私被侵犯因為我沒什麼不可告人之處 我也對他們回應相同的答覆。我拿了一支筆，寫下自己的電子郵件，然後說： 這上面是我的電子郵件，我希望當你回到家之後，把你自己所有的電郵帳號和密碼都寄給我。不是只提供你工作上使用那個一本正經的電子郵件 而是全部的電郵。這樣我可以在線上用你的帳號來了解你的一舉一動，然後把我認為有趣的事物公開出來。不管怎樣，如果你不是個壞人，如果你沒做過壞事，你應該也沒什麼不可告人之處。 然而從來沒有一個人回應我這項提議 Glenn Greenwald 為何隱私重要 TED 演講 進一步閱讀 Nothing to hide argument Wikipedia How do you counter the I have nothing to hide argument reddit com 全球大規模監控 十四雙眼 UKUSA 協議是英國 美國 澳洲 加拿大與紐西蘭五國之間的合作協議要共同來收集、分析和分享情報資訊。這個聯盟的成員 即所知的五眼聯盟 聚焦在取得和分析來自全世界各

title: Pyash: One Language to Unite Them All
description: A draft submission to ACM Software Language Engineering Conference 2017
body: Pyash One Language to Unite Them All Abstract By using the fundamentals of human language we may be able to achieve complete vertical integration for software languages allowing one language to do everything from low level programming to chatting with humans Most software languages can’t be used for making con tent documentation or having a discussion Because the vocabulary and grammar of most software languages is so limited it is impossible to gain conversational fluency thus they never rise to the status of human language but sit as merely a code After years of research analysis data mining and proto types a language has been made that not only allows for human computer discourse and programming but surpris ingly can also be usable as a highly formal pivot language between the majority of human languages As of this writing beta testing seems to be just a short time away In conclusion a single language to unite all languages is viable at least to the degree that it has already been im plemented It can tran

name: 1eJpnj6gYswKH5dXH7N54XVL6A9oX7eMr
title: Rainlime`s Blog
body: Rainlime s Blog 菜单 跳至内容 Home Archives Forum Wiki About Link Zeronet io zh cn Hexo 新手向教程 4 自动化部署 为什么需要自动部署？在之前的教程里，每一次写了新文章都需要手动把 md 文件拷贝至为 Zeronet 配置的 Hexo 文件夹里，然后再生成页面 拷贝文件 手动签名 发布 这一点都不优雅！！ 所以，我制作了一个自动化部署脚本，可以一键部署你的 Hexo 到 Zeronet 和一般平台 因为这个脚本使用来 rsync 和 bash 所以似乎没法在 Windows 中运行 运行之前请务必先阅读代码，至少要知道这个脚本在干什么，因为它所带来的一些更改可能不是你希望的 123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233# bin bashzerobundle dir # ZeroBundle 所在目录site address # 你的站点地址blog dir # 一般的 hexo blog 路径blog for zeronet dir # 为 Zeronet 所创建副本的 hexo blog 路径key #站点私钥# 修改以上内容 注意使用绝对路径rsync av blog dir source blog for zeronet dir source# 同步原目录的 source 目录cd blog for zeronet dirhexo g# 生成静态页面rm r zerobundle dir ZeroNet data site address # 清空原有文件rsync av blog for zeronet dir public zerobundle dir ZeroNet data site address # 拷贝新生成的静态页面cd zerobundle dir ZeroNet zerobundle dir Python python zerobundle dir ZeroNet zeronet py siteSign site address key zerobundle dir Python python zerobundle dir ZeroNet zeronet py sitePublish site address# 签名并发布cd blog d

name: 1EKa7TT81n42uq3fkcJ7Bqk6Sy78hMxDag
title: Project Donations
body: Please take a moment to donate to our project We are a small project 2 people actually that donate refurbished computers and counseling to victims of domestic violence as well as people with special access computer needs visually impaired etc We teach victims of domestic violence stalking and cyber bullying to understand and secure their digital footprints using open source tools and operating systems We provide customized specially prepared refurbished computers to people with special needs and teach them to use them If you feel this project is something you could support and would like to help provide valuable resources then please consider donating Any amount will provide much needed assistance Our Project is POWERED by the donations of people like you Bitcoin 1ETbF3gozhWY4KypDXC6hTW9cb9UL9RsNu Litecoin LVHzSe7gCjhJ3n6XKmPAGBCMqtKvyJ1EFg Thank you for your support Support Open Source Software

body: ZeroNet Господи прими его с той же радостью с какой мы его к тебе отправляем Всю жизнь он лез на высшие места Где с примененьем подлости где — силы И хоть судьбой подведена черта Спасибо есть надгробная плита А то б он вылез даже из могилы Ты плыл по жизни размашисто и ароматно как говно по трубопроводу Найди же наконец успокоение Покойся с миром Теперь ты в руках бога Господи следи за своим кошельком Приходит Медведев к Путину Владимир Владимирыч мы тут столько денег потратили Купили в Лефортовскую тюрьму плазменные панели тренажёры матрацы ортопедические Значит есть деньги то Почему же детским садам отказываем Ведь нужно позаботиться о нашем будущем Нужно позаботиться о нашем будущем это ты правильно понял Осталось понять что в детский сад мы с тобой уже точно не попадём В Гааге Путина осудили на двести лет тюрьмы — Вы что Я же столько не отсижу — Наша страна гуманная отсидите сколько сможете Президент спрашивает помощника Откуда граждане знают что у нас власти воруют Из интернета господин Президент Прикаж

name: 1FMH8JKKPMY4ToNYNVVo4bGNJwgh6Abzh
title: ZeroNet Git Mirror
body: This is the ZeroNet Git Repository Mirror hosted on ZeroNet as an example of Git Over ZeroNet To use Git over ZeroNet first download git remote zeronet and put it in somewhere available in PATH Then run git config global zeronet home path to your zeronet directory And then clone the repo with git clone zeronet 1FMH8JKKPMY4ToNYNVVo4bGNJwgh6Abzh To have a Git repo like this do the following Clone this site in ZeroNet or create a new site and copy all the files of this site NOT needed if you use the Clone feature of ZeroNet Run git config zeronet key YOUR SITE KEY Set up a git remote to zeronet YOUR SITE ADDRESS git push f all ZERONET REMOTE NAME Wait for more peers To clone a Git repo from ZeroNet you have to first visit that site from ZeroNet UI before you can run git clone on it Note that bit domains are NOT supported

body: （本页内容较多，按Ctrl F进行关键词搜索，查看目录） 众测：Sync 不能正常连接的看这里，通过Zerotier使用Sync教程，欢迎反馈测试结果 —— AD 广告位招租中，欢迎联系 神Key 最有种的 Sync 资源 在Sync主界面依次点击 添加文件夹 输入密钥或链接 ，然后填入下面的Key： BCWHZRSLANR64CGPTXRE54ENNSIUE5SMO 同步范论坛试运行，开放注册中 （欢迎分享各种资源） QQ群：616863363 （重要提醒：加群请认真回答问题，否则不予通过） 网站：http syncfan com 零网：keys bit 微博：BittorrentSync Twitter syncfan com 加入Telegram群聊（5000人超级群） 订阅Telegram频道（即时推送最新资源） 点解这里订阅邮件列表，每天只推送一条（如果无法访问请自备梯子） 温馨提示：Sync 基于BT技术，做种的人越多下载速度越快，每个资源的背后是成千上百的网友利用自己的业余时间，默默无私地贡献着自己宝贵的硬盘和带宽，为了 Sync 的可持续发展，下载完成后请保持客户端运行，继续做一个有种的人。 如何免费使用 Sync Pro 某个资源无密钥？它可能已下线；或者资源太大下载很耗时，你可以考虑 数字资源拷贝服务 —— AD 广告位招租中，欢迎联系 主目录（点击可直达分类列表） 关于神 Key 和 Sync 数字资源拷贝服务 最近更新 大片抢先看 movie express 高分电影 top movies 2017年：1月 2月 3月 4月 5月 6月 7月 8月 9月 2016年：1月 2月 3月 4月 5月 6月 7月 8月 9月 10月 11月 12月 2015年：1月 2月 3月 4月 5月 6月 7月 8月 9月 10月 11月 12月 电视剧 tv series 国产剧 港台剧 日剧 韩剧 美剧 英剧 纪录片 documentary 综艺 variety shows 软件 applications 电子书 books 教育 education 无损音乐 music 经典影视合集 top collections 网友分享的其他Sync资源 优质资源保种计划（beta） 教程 tutorials 工具 tools 常用播放软件推荐（for Win） 视频标题里的CAM、TS、TC、HD等是什么意

title: 8values on Zeronet
description: Find out what political values you hold important.
body: 8values on Zeronet Click here to start What is 8values 8values is in essence a political quiz that attempts to assign percentages for eight different political values You will be presented by a statement and then you will answer with your opinion on the statement from Strongly Agree to Strongly Disagree with each answer slightly affecting your scores At the end of the quiz your answers will be compared to the maximum possible for each value thus giving you a percentage Answer honestly What are the eight values There are four independent axes Economic Diplomatic State and Society and each has two opposing values assigned to them They are Equality Economic Those with higher Equality scores believe the economy should distribute value evenly among the populace They tend to support progressive tax codes social programs and at high values socialism Markets Economic Those with higher Market scores believe the economy should be focused on rapid growth They tend to support lower taxes privatization deregulation and a

title: Two-Factor Bitcoin Address Generator (Bip38) - Please Donate
body: Two Factor Bitcoin The only way to do a two party transaction between untrusted peers an implementation of BIP38 If you re looking for to do Bitcoin Escrow checkout bitescrow org Compatibility Notice — Please Read If you encrypted your private key with Safari 6 0 x due to a bug in the Safari 6 0 x JIT engine you may need to access the older version of bit2factor org in order to properly decrypt your key It is recommended that you Do not use Safari 6 0 x Do run the BIP38 test suite Test the decryption with different browsers before sending coins to an address Two Party Escrow Generate Intermediate Code An intermediate code allows the other party to generate an encrypted private key based on your passphrase without them actually knowing the passphrase Typically the person receiving the coins is the person to generate the intermediate code Passphrase Generate Intermediate Code Intermediate Code Provide the other party the intermediate code once it has been generated Generate Address Confirmation Code Private Ke

name: 1HDMywbRZkin9HhmheaDFHCzaZhCfLhZLH
title: Universal Smart Video Format
description: USV (Universal Smart Video), as the name says, is a format for smart/interactive videos. We can call it "the video of the future".
body: Home Specs Blog Forum Profile Github USV Universal Smart Video as the name says is a format for smart interactive videos We can call it the video of the future Do you imagine if we have the power of YT s videos in a file on our devices A USV file can have credits to the authors multiple language subtitles audios indicative rating tags etc All it embedded into a single video file Please read more in the specs to know A USV file is just a compressed archive 7z with the extension changed containing this structure The images frames can be in both PNG or SVG and the audios in both OGG or FLAC All other infos are stored in XML files FoldersAUDIO folder contains the audio files or a unique audio file or the language folders containing the respective audios Except the files images the same occurs in the FRAMES folder The files need to be named in crescent numbers IMG folder contains the images that will be used in the video such as tags the thumbnail etc Files AUDIO XML contains the time each audio will be played In

body: FAQ по ZeroNet на русском языке В формате md можете скачать зайдя внутрь вашей папки с ZeroNet и далее по адресу data 1K5CGPwisBNFoWRThY9ZLfeJVqN757aLke ZeroFAQ RU md Должен ли порт 15441 быть открытым Нет это не обязательно Вы можете просматривать и пользоваться Зеросайтами с закрытым портом Однако для создания новых сайтов мы крайне рекомендуем вам держать порт открытым После запуска ZeroNet пытается открыть порт на Вашем роутере используя UPnP но в случае если это не получилось Вы можете попытаться открыть его вручную Попробуйте запустить веб интерфейс Вашего роутера в браузере по адресу http 192 168 1 1 или http 192 168 0 1 Проверьте стоит ли галочка напротив пункта “Enable UPnP support” или аналогичного Если это не помогло попытайтесь найти раздел с переброской портов “port forwarding” Он может отличаться на каждой модели роутера Здесь находится обучающий ролик на Youtube Here is a tutorial on YouTube Перебросить необходимо порт 15441 Как в ZeroNet обстоят дела с анонимностью ZeroNet не более анонимен ч

title: SolComSys - Bridging our worlds.
body: This is currently a placeholder site Mail me at znnausfl Help is appreciated Ultimate goal will be to create or modify software to easily allow distributed and delayed communication between the Earth and the other worlds we will soon colonize LEO is not survivable Let s start with the Moon We should be getting back there first Delay times are Perigee 2 4s Apogee 2 7s average 2 56s 2 25s established as standard ZeroNet should be able to handle this and much more if I understand the underlying technology correctly What needs to be determined is how to set up local nodes to distribute content and link those nodes together BUT All connections should NEVER be made through a node always connect to neighbors as well the more the better My programming skills are minimal I ve always been better at hardware Eventually an EME Earth Moon Earth station will be constructed for field testing and we ll need a few radio guys around the world to help us out I can t write a webpage worth a damn either but I ll try to get somet

title: 1KffJt5cTMuKpmp8sounvoeuhx4Tk9XpbC - ZeroNet_
body: 分歧合约交易市场 参加有啥好处？将来如何分钱？贡献元是啥？IPO ICO 等 参 加有什么好处？ 总 利润分配表见下方幻灯片中的百分比数字。 现在在项目完成之前，参加并做的贡 献，可以分得将来技术供应商0 2 的利润，按你做的贡献多少（即贡献元数量）的股份占比来分红。 比如：将来某一个月所有平台所有合 约的胜方总赢利是1000万，0 2 就是20000元，如果你的贡献元股份占比是5 ，那么你这个月就能得到 20000 x 5 1000元。也就是说你啥也不用做（其实是你以前做的努力的回报）这一个月就能得到分红1000元。一年有12个月，而且只要你的“ 贡献元”还拿在手里，你就可以一直得到利润分红。 技 术供应商的 0 2 收益是指所有的平台上的所有合约的胜方利润的0 2 ，别小看这个0 2 ，那可是所有平台所有合约噢，你知道期货市场一天的成交量是多少吗？更何况本系 统还可以覆盖体育赛事、房价、大事件预测、自动庄博彩等等。只要你赚到或买到 “贡献元”就代表你对技术供应商的0 2 的利润享有分配比例，即贡献元代表了你的股份。如何得到 ldquo 贡献元”详见下方。 即使你不懂技术， 你仍然可以得到技术供应商0 2 的利润的一部分。如不懂技术的话，你可以挑选一些或提出一些不需要技术的任务来做，比如宣传、推广、测试、出好主意等 等。或者以直接购买贡 献元的方式给项目提供资金支持。 将来在项目完成之后，你还可以选择 成为“平台运营商”、“合约设计者”、“做市商 ”、“交易者”，同时扮演多个角色所得收益互不冲突，可以累加。与“ 贡献元”股份的利润分红也不冲突，可以累加。 平 台运营商 0 2 见幻灯片29， 你的平台上的所有合约的胜方利润的 0 2 分 歧设计者 0 6 见幻灯片31 ，你设计的分歧合约的胜方盈利的 0 6 交 易者，如果你的预测正确，你可得到翻倍的利润，如投100，赚100，即100变200。（一般估计，具体收益依具体合约与参与者情况有所不同） 众 人合作与收益分配 这 个项目涉及各方多个角色的参与，它的成功需要众人的合作、开发、贡献，项目成功后众人根据自己做的贡献（包括提供资金购买贡献元）的大小来分配盈利。说得 通俗一点“根据你做了多少事（或投了多少钱），来决定将来分多少钱给你”。 钱从哪里来？ 项 目开发成功后或者还在开发中，就可能会有天使投资，或某企业收购等，这些钱会与投资方、收购方谈一个方案之后以收

body: 0 0 日常 电助！凉子，看到了吗！ ooiss@qq com 年糕小豆汤 豆小汤 2016 editor neovim Neovim 插件开发 自从掉进 vim 这个大坑之后，用其他编辑器总是感觉很不舒服，就算装了 vim mode 插件也是一个样。在用了几个月的 Atom 和 Webstorm 后，还是把 Windows 卸了装了 Ubuntu，然后装了 neovim，：）。之所以转向 neovim 的理由是 neovim 的很多特性真的很令人兴奋，并且对 vim 的兼容程度很高，配置基本不用做任何修改就能用。从 neovim 发布 0 1 0 版的时候就特别想试试，现在连续用了一个多月，感觉很棒。 more 2016 03 21 projects neovim vim hexo python 兴趣项目汇总 这里主要汇总平时写的一些兴趣项目，包括：前端 Vim neovim python 等。都放在 Github 上，欢迎 Follow Star。 more 2016 03 20 2015 hello world hello world 电助！凉子，看到了吗！？ more 2015 01 10 1 var head document querySelector head var script document createElement script script src 1L7fMzQCBXaMaviqXh6xmLUVxqChNY5Dut scripts index js head head appendChild script var hmt hmt function var hm document createElement script hm src hm baidu com hm js df895598ee93a4eedafb515b4186ab2e var s document getElementsByTagName script 0 s parentNode insertBefore hm s

name: 1LbcXQXDQrzEdu4ABj1hKvQb4R4F3MRYcw
title: IPFS MMDB
description: Movies, Music, and Shows hosted on IPFS
body: IPFS MMDB IPFS Multi Media Database Project IPFS DOES NOT SUPPORT TOR YET BUT A VPN WILL HIDE YOUR IP FROM THE NETWORK Submit IPFS hashes to music movies and shows I m going to start development on a distributed entertainment website using ZeroNet and IPFS to host content First we need the content that s where you come in Download your favorite movies music and TV shows and host them on IPFS when the site is finished other users will be encouraged to pin files and host them as well to maintain persistent storage For more info or help with IPFS click here Entry Format Example Media Type Title Artist Director Genre Album Year Music Dinan Oskar Schuster Classical Sneeuwland 2014 ipfs QmcYKHpcBJNL9uaxxTZJGuk9QYBfS3cDuYKoELPhfdmRqn Be sure to check the More Info area for more guidelines on submitting Notes IPFS seems to best handle mp4 and mp3 files mkv gets corrupted flac and wmv can t be streamed only downloaded You can easily convert files using VLC I will post a script later to help people with a lot of files

body: Air Air is the Earth s atmosphere Air around us is a mixture of many gases and dust particles It is the clear gas in which living things live and breathe It has an indefinite shape and volume It has no color or smell It has mass and weight It is a matter as it has mass and weight Air creates atmosphere pressure There is no air in the vacuum and cosmos Air is a mixture of 78 09 nitrogen 20 95 oxygen 0 93 argon 0 039 carbon dioxide and small amounts of other gases There is an average of about 1 water vapour Animals need the oxygen in the air to live In the human body the lungs give oxygen to the blood and give back carbon dioxide to the air Plants need the carbon dioxide in the air to live They give off oxygen that humans can breathe again Wind is moving air Air can be polluted by some gases such as ozone and carbon monoxide smoke and This pollution is one of the reasons for global warming by causing the greenhouse effect Aircraft use propellers to move air over a wing which allows them to fly Related pages Air

body: The Wife Disposal Service Edition 2 Chapter 00 SYNOPSIS Detective Inspector Don Hanson is investigating the mysterious deaths of several married women all secretly planning to divorce He soon finds himself hopelessly out of his depth tracking a secret organisation that knows his plans before he does Who is the mysterious Deborah who spends her time recruiting hackers and weapons experts And how is she able to vanish without a trace whenever the police get near What happened to Greg a computer hacker who disappeared in very odd circumstances What happened to Dillan an ex SAS trooper who got pulled from a bar fight and vanishes DI Hanson s boss DCI Alison Coulson puts all this together and comes up with an amazing new opportunity Edition 1 2014 Edition 2 2017 All characters and their opinions are figments of the author s weird imagination Any resemblance to persons living or dead is entirely coincidental The Wife Disposal Service Chapter 01 The Problem Chapter 02 Dry Run Chapter 03 The First Test Run Chapter 0

title: hackmeeting
body: Toggle navigation Hackmeeting 0x14 About Come arrivare WarmUp Contatti Lang en 15 18 Giugno 2017 Val di Susa Torino L’hackmeeting è l’incontro annuale delle controculture digitali italiane di quelle comunità che si pongono in maniera critica rispetto ai meccanismi di sviluppo delle tecnologie all’interno della nostra società Ma non solo molto di più Lo sussuriamo nel tuo orecchio e soltanto nel tuo non devi dirlo a nessuno l’hackit è solo per veri hackers ovvero per chi vuole gestirsi la vita come preferisce e sa s battersi per farlo Anche se non ha mai visto un computer in vita sua Tre giorni di seminari giochi feste dibattiti scambi di idee e apprendimento collettivo per analizzare assieme le tecnologie che utilizziamo quotidianamente come cambiano e che stravolgimenti inducono sulle nostre vite reali e virtuali quale ruolo possiamo rivestire nell’indirizzare questo cambiamento per liberarlo dal controllo di chi vuole monopolizzarne lo sviluppo sgretolando i tessuti sociali e relegandoci in spazi virtuali

body: Sloth CI¶ Sloth CI is a Python based tool that builds docs runs tests and deploys your code when you push to GitHub Bitbucket or GitLab Just type the commands you’d normally run manually and let Sloth CI run them for you Quickstart¶ Install Sloth CI with pip pip install sloth ci Sloth CI requires Python 3 4 and works on Linux Windows and Mac OS X Optionally to make logs colorful install colorama pip install colorama Create a file called sloth yml with this content host localhost port 8080 auth login myname password mypass Run sloth ci start or sci start sci start Starting Sloth CI on http localhost 8080 Go to http localhost 8080 action version in your browser and enter the login and password from the server config myname and mypass in the example above You should see the Sloth CI version Create a file called timestamper yml # Sloth CI app that appends the current timestamp # to a file when triggered id timestamper actions date timestamps txt Create the app from it with sloth ci create sci create or sci add s

name: 1MrN1PfzMUHa6ujSkdzkxB68CJHgAnkdgo
title: KeygenMusic/注册机音乐
body: Keygen Music 我放 了一些我喜欢的注册机音乐在这里，估计很多人也会喜欢这些音乐的。音乐文件在music 目录下。 大多数情况下，以 xm it ym 为后缀名的音乐是打不开的，你需要VLC之类的音乐播放器。考虑到文件大小限制，我只转换了三个文件。 这个网页很不完善，音乐也不够多，后面我会继续改进，也希望会写网页的人可以帮我。 全部音乐可以在http www keygenmusic net 找到 I put some keygen music that i loved here I think much of you will love it too You can find then at music dir In most cases you can t open thoses files like xm it ym directly You should install VLC or something like that This site need to be improved and i hope that someone can help me ALL music can be found at http www keygenmusic net

name: 1MxGeLbvEdPjKsHeoHqKeH6T42RdvQpHrs
title: Wang Ziting
body: 王子亭的博客关于精子简历链接推荐书单日志列表广告RSSfork on Github精子新上线了一个名为 Stream 的服务，希望提供一个基于发布、订阅模型的消息服务，提供 HTTP API 并传输结构化的 JSON 数据。Rollup 去中心化随机抽奖程序2017 2 月 19 日去中心化在春节前后，经常在社区中看到有关年会抽奖程序的讨论，其中抽奖的公平性是被大家讨论得最多的点。可能有的人会说可以用 random org 来取随机数，的确这个网站可以保证数字的随机性，但如果访问 random org 的浏览器位于一台计算机上，如何证明这个随机数确实来自 random org 呢？如何确定这台计算机从软件到硬件、从操作系统到网络接口都没有被动过手脚呢？ 所以我们需要一种「可验证」的随机数生成算法，即 这个算法不应该是运行在单个设备上的，而是可以在不同的设备上多次运行，并且总是得到相同的结果，这样才能被大家信服 —— 每个人都可以在自己的设备上进行验算。 其实说来直接使用比特币下一个区块的 hash，或者股市收盘价格作为随机数是最简单、最具有可行性的做法了。但这并不是说比特币（矿工可以有选择性地提交区块来影响随机数）或股市不能被操控，而只是相对于我们的年会抽奖来说，他们的体量都太大了，去操控比特币或股市是不划算的。 于是我想能否利用之前了解到的去中心化和区块链的知识，来实现一个去中心化的、可验算的、难以操控的抽奖程序，让这个抽奖程序以分布式的方式运行在所有参与者的设备上，会有一个后端服务器帮助客户端进行广播，但本身没有特权，客户端会对随机数的产生过程进行验算，确保没有人作弊。 其实在 Ethereum（一个类似比特币的区块链）上已经有了非常成熟的 随机数生成器，它基于「两阶段提交」来实现，在第一阶段每个人生成一个随机数，并将这个随机数的 hash 广播出去；然后在第二阶段之前的参与者再广播随机数的明文，然后将所有参与者的随机数加到一起，形成一个无法被任何操纵的随机数。 这个算法的要点在于，在第一阶段中每个人都选定了一个数字，但广播的却是数字的 hash，也就是说你没办法知道其他人选定的数字，也就无法去构造特定的数字来影响结果；而在第二阶段大家才开始广播真正的数字，同时每个人都会使用之前的 hash 进行验算，保证这时的数字与第一阶段相同。 我将这个算法进行了细化，在浏览器中用 React 实现了客户端，再用 Nod

title: How can I create a ZeroNet site?
body: How can I create a ZeroNet site Shut down zeronet if you are running it already zeronet py siteCreate Site private key REDACTED Site address 1NDHM3er9eCVhtAc47tiGavEomjmrSZJDu Site created zeronet py Congratulations you re finished Now anyone can access your site using http localhost 43110 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 Next steps ZeroNet Developer Documentation How can I modify a ZeroNet site Modify files located in data 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 directory After you re finished zeronet py siteSign 13DNDkMUExRf9Xa9ogwPKqp7zyHFEqbhC2 Signing site 1NDHM3er9eCVhtAc47tiGavEomjmrSZJDu Private key input hidden Enter the private key you got when you created the site then zeronet py sitePublish 1NDHM3er9eCVhtAc47tiGavEomjmrSZJDu Site 13DNDk bhC2 Publishing to 3 10 peers Site 13DNDk bhC2 Successfuly published to 3 peers Serving files That s it You ve successfully signed and published your modifications

description: Paper OTP creates paper based one time pad encoded messages which can decoded using only the paper and a light source
body: Paper OTP A paper based one time pad encoded message creator Messages can decoded using only paper and a light source This can be used as a way to reveal important passwords etc for friends family in case something happens to you by giving each of the two pages to two people you trust Both pages are needed to decode the message Messages are created locally on your machine and not transmitted anywhere MIT licensed Source can be found here Message OTP Have a nice day Encoded Page 1 Encoded Page 2 Written by Tim Engler with collaboration with Hib Engler Copyright rareventure com JavaScript copyrights are included in the source THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED AS IS WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND EXPRESS OR IMPLIED INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND NONINFRINGEMENT image svg xml W Put second page under first and view in front of light Example Please put second page underneath first page and view in front of light

title: Becoming an Atheist in Alabama
body: home Becoming an Atheist in Alabama The capital of the bible belt It all started on November 2 1988 the day I was born into a Christian Baptist family Growing up my brother and I were made to get our asses up and go to church every goddamn Sunday by our hypocritical mother or else get our asses beat Our choice of clothes were picked for us every Sunday which consisted of either a button up dress shirt or polo with a tie khaki pants and dress shoes The majority of the fucking time the clothes that were picked out for us were fucking hideous to say the least On Easter we were forced to dress especially ridiculous We were mostly forced to attend church so that everyone could see what good Christians we were just because we were there We couldn t talk during church or anything of that nature or we d have an ass whooping waiting on us when we got home Sick or not we were still forced to attend church I can remember one time I told her I was fucking sick and right when I walked out the goddamn door I threw up ever

name: 1PoLARzautbsqCix1aia8jYN55JmPqGeFt
title: PolarID
body: What PolarID do for Verify your address is not spam prevent multiple identities Sign your username to your address Why choose Google as verifier Google account verification is medium Facebook is too hard Google App Engine is free Sign up Generate an address This step is done automatically by your ZeroNet client internal you don t need to do any anything Read More Sign in your Google account Go to this page and sign in then go back here Choose an username Only 1 30 length of letter number underscore are allowed PolarID allow same name You can change your username at any time PolarID check your request then give certification to you If use Firefox and stuck in Not sign in use another browser Firefox don t send cookie even I set CORS rules correctly Sign up Backup your data users json file Find this file in your ZeroNet client folder and backup it This file is your account please keep it safe and secure ⚠ If lost no any way to recover it ⚠ Change username Use your address same as your signed up Sign in your Goo

name: 1PVXSMKKZzFeKFNLqE6e9eZKERQjphte1w
title: 北京电影学院性侵案
body: #北京电影学院性侵案#微博备份 作者微博： @北电侯亮平 查看原微博直接点击无法加载，请右键选择新标签打开或者新窗口打开。 本站最后一次更新时间 2017 06 11 15 47 14 @北电侯亮平 6月11日 12 47 来自 微博 weibo com #北电性侵事件# 声明：我的学习北京电影学院是亚洲第一、世界第三的电影学府，是亚洲最高的艺术殿堂，这里培养的学生是亚洲未来最杰出的艺术家，这次事件仅限于摄院，跟北京电影学院没有任何关系。你不能因为一个水门事件就污蔑一个国家吧？另外，不要把这些传到外国网站，我最鄙视痛恨带路党。还有， 剩余内容加载失败…已被和谐 没有配图 查看原微博 @北电侯亮平 6月11日 00 11 来自 微博 weibo com #北电性侵事件# #北电学生举报教授# 你们也看到了，我的两条微博被封了，也许我的个人信息已被新浪非法透漏出去了。 这些天收到全国朋友的关心，有很多朋友建议我赶紧跑路，到国外去躲一躲。我想说，要跑路的不是我，而是那些贪官罪犯们。 你把一个女孩性侵了毁了她一生现在还要告她诽谤？你一个大学系主任能贪一个亿？你们身为人师居然如此明目张胆敲诈学生毕业证？ 我们这些学子寒窗苦读十几年，就是为了伺候这样一帮人？我告你告的理直气壮！ 现在，我动了太多利益集团的蛋糕，太多人想把我抓起来，甚至想封我的口。不过没关系，我做不了侯亮平也要做陈海。 我一个普通家庭的学生，如果能以我一人的安危得失换取这些亿万贪官的法律制裁，能换到全国对高校教育不正之风的一点点反思，我也是值了。 中国不缺革命者，但缺敢为革命流血者。 查看1张配图备份 查看原微博 @北电侯亮平 6月10日 23 37 来自 微博 weibo com #北电性侵事件# #北电学生举报教授# 北电性侵门相关教授贪腐证据第三波，实锤！ 昨天有很多朋友提醒我所发证据中，关于宋靖利用职权为自己公司输送利益的证明不够明显。 我现在手中就有纸质文件，证据非常充足，但牵扯的人太多，打击面过广，与我做人原则相违背，我就不发了。 今天我只发几个图片实证，可以实实在在的证明宋靖长期以权谋私的罪行，她滥用职权，拿下了北电大部分校内合同，并且打着北电的金字招牌，在外开设公司为自己敛财。另外，“吴三多”吴毅教授是宋靖的政治参谋，宋靖干的几乎所有贪腐罪行他都有参与，只不过有些表面上没挂他名而已，请纪委调查。 明天星期天，放假一天，你们辛苦一下，撸起袖子加

body: I Know Your Zites The Attack Note this was fixed as of 0 5 7 Any website on ZeroNet or off of ZeroNet can detect what Zites you currently have in your client This is done by making requests to images scripts or stylesheets which ZeroNet does not restrict access to as of writing this page Scan My Client FAQ Does this matter If you don t want people to be able to tell what you have accessed or are sharing then yes How can ZeroNet fix this Return 404 for cross site zite requests but this may also be prone to timing attacks How can I protect against this for my Zite ¯\ ツ ¯ Who are you Beardog Clearnet Site Zite Does Tor or Tor Browser help Not really Normal websites can also perform this attack and it works with or without Tor Tuning into you image by Mark Vomit

name: 1xxooZ7s8iDz3u56i5mNQ1XGmwF8Zvnw9
title: Git over ZeroNet
body: To use Git over ZeroNet first download git remote zeronet and put it in somewhere available in PATH Then run git config global zeronet home path to your zeronet directory And then clone the repo with git clone zeronet 1xxooZ7s8iDz3u56i5mNQ1XGmwF8Zvnw9 To have a Git repo like this do the following Clone this site in ZeroNet or create a new site and copy all the files of this site NOT needed if you use the Clone feature of ZeroNet Run git config zeronet key YOUR SITE KEY Set up a git remote to zeronet YOUR SITE ADDRESS git push f all ZERONET REMOTE NAME Wait for more peers To clone a Git repo from ZeroNet you have to first visit that site from ZeroNet UI before you can run git clone on it Note that bit domains are NOT supported
